                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="46095" author="pjones" created="Sun, 7 Oct 2012 07:23:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for 2.4&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="46056" author="nrutman" created="Fri, 5 Oct 2012 13:58:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If all threads are blocked (e.g. waiting for lock callbacks) except for the one remaining HP thread, then the hpreq_ratio mechanism will prevent more than &lt;em&gt;ratio&lt;/em&gt; HP rpc&apos;s from being handled, thus preventing this last thread from doing anything.&lt;br/&gt;
This absolutely is &lt;em&gt;not&lt;/em&gt; a minor issue; it will completely stall your server.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
